item.title: SFRaves Home Page
item.description:
SFRaves Home Page

SFRaves is an electronic virtual community of ravers, networking together around the clock, sharing information and ideas, and inspiring one another. The mailing list started in 1992 and has over 2500 members from all parts of the community and all parts of the world, with a focus of discussion toward the greater San Francisco Bay Area.
